	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Front-end for the `dotfiles` CLI in the dotfiles repo.

Type `dotfiles` in Alfred, then:
  theme &lt;name&gt;      switch theme (Tab to drill in)
  wallpaper &lt;name&gt;  set wallpaper only
  random            random theme
  update            git pull + re-apply theme
  sync              re-run install.sh
  doctor            check symlinks and dependencies
  save              commit + push the repo

The workflow shells out to ~/.local/bin/dotfiles, so it always tracks the repo.
</string>
